    body: 'In 1917, the Blessed Virgin Mary appeared six times to three shepherd children in Fatima, Portugal, delivering messages that included calls for daily Rosary prayer, penance for sinners, and consecration of Russia to her Immaculate Heart. The apparitions included the Miracle of the Sun, witnessed by tens of thousands. The three secrets of Fatima contain prophetic elements about wars, persecution, and the ultimate triumph of the Immaculate Heart.',
